Adam held her chair for her. \'93You haven\'92t met Mr. Hamilton, dear,\'94 he said. \
She held out her hand. \'93How do you do,\'94 she said. \
Samuel had been inspecting her. \'93It\'92s a beautiful face,\'94 he said, \'93I\'92m glad to meet you. You are well, I hope?\'94 \
\'93Oh, yes. Yes, I\'92m well.\'94 \
