\'93Come on,\'94 she said at last. \'93You got something\'97what is it?\'94 \
\'93Well, it ain\'92t much. I don\'92t know what to think of it.\'94 \'93Don\'92t think. Just tell. I\'92ll think,\'94 she said sharply. \'93Might not even be true.\'94\uc0\u8232 \'93For Christ\'92s sake!\'94 she said angrily. \
\'93Well, I talked to the last guy that seen her. Guy named Joe, like me\'97\'94 \
